Template-HTML
=====================

A wrapper aroudn Template Toolkit to provide automatic encoding of HTML
entities in template.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    Template

